{"tid":1967082,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"IG咁仆街多數扮睇唔到，我地要向間Fact Check公司投訴施壓","createTime":"2020-04-10T15:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T16:50:43.000Z","uid":211994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64fcf21fd2e34849f1c0144b33e61b9663cad55c","tid":1967082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"唔知可唔可行，不過大家一齊試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢主要都係話因為幅相執過嚟，所以可能會有誤導成分<br />\n咁如果我地證明到<span style=\"color: red;\">執相只係修飾，事實上真係有咁多人去遊行</span>嘅話，會唔會可以解除到佢個限制呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKkLNzJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKkLNzJ.png&h=a1570675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該係個間公司嘅Twitter，有冇英文好嘅手足可以幫下拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AFPFactCheck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAFPFactCheck&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479Va%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=c3bd7468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AFPFactCheck</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XdA9N9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XdA9N9.png&h=7079da6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動目的：<br />\n證明張相冇誤導成分<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n搵當日遊行嘅照片（最好嚟自各大傳媒）去證明，個日真係好多人遊行<br />\n作者攞返張原圖出嚟做證明<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下，係咁tag instagram真係冇咩用"},{"pid":"2bc595b27147a985c934b5ea84566f558e33c598","tid":1967082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b5c9b1c62b4336c59d935f091f7089c11644fe0","tid":1967082,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d6d1503f32975294525210c0881bafe5e8f86a5","tid":1967082,"uid":211994